# Loaded automatically by Vitest (mode "test") — NOT by any real build.
#
# The demo's apiBase() (src/api.ts) throws when VITE_DEMO_API_BASE is unset,
# which is correct for a misconfigured deployment but silently derails tests:
# e.g. useTextToSpeech's backend-voice-priority specs mock global fetch and
# assert it gets called, but speakViaBackend() catches the apiBase() throw
# and returns "not configured" before fetch is ever reached — failing the
# assertions for a reason that has nothing to do with the code under test.
# Any syntactically valid URL works; tests mock fetch, nothing is contacted.
VITE_DEMO_API_BASE=http://demo-api.test
